	   Foote Cone handles advertising for Nabisco cookie brands like
Oreos, Chips Ahoy! and SnackWells as well as Life Savers candy and
Fleischmann's, Bluebonnet and Parkay margarines and spreads.
	   McCann-Erickson is responsible for Ritz, Triscuits, Wheat Thins
and other crackers from Nabisco.
	   ``Lowe certainly created some memorable advertising,'' Barrows
said, ``But we have to stay focused on the bottom line.''
